        <mxCell id="W8QUFkcHTBao64T8szoz-38" value="&lt;b&gt;Next Steps:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;Flesh out the content of the Default Logger to include a queue or other multi-threading coping mechanism&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Going to use an object structure for logger definition as the template string only works after C++ 20&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Going to specify format flags directly in ILogFormatter (actually, thinking OO, perhaps it should be in a separate class)&lt;/div&gt;" style="shape=note2;boundedLbl=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;size=25;verticalAlign=top;align=center;" parent="1" vertex="1">
